# Dataset — Streaming Service Customer Data

This project uses the **Streaming Service Dataset** from Kaggle.

## Download

🔗 [Kaggle Dataset Link](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/akashanandt/streaming-service-data)

You will need a free Kaggle account to download.

## Setup

After downloading, place the file in this folder as follows:

```
data/
└── streaming_service_data.csv
```

## Features Used

| Feature | Type | Used For |
|---------|------|----------|
| Age | Numerical | Regression, Clustering |
| Subscription Length | Numerical | Regression |
| Support Tickets Raised | Numerical | Regression |
| Satisfaction Score | Numerical | Regression (best single predictor) |
| Discount Offered | Numerical | Regression |
| Last Activity | Numerical | Regression |
| Monthly Spend | Numerical | **Target variable** |
| Churn | Binary | **Classification target** |
| Gender | Categorical | Regression (encoded) |
| Region | Categorical | Regression (encoded) |
| Payment Method | Categorical | Regression (encoded) |
